column5: Hey everyone i just wanted everyone to know i have started a new online business called four bros outdoors. my company has unbeatable prices  and service. online only at this time but i do have a place in brampton if you would like to pick up items we carry all types of fishing gear and add new products daily if you are looking for a product that i do not currently have on my website please feel free to shoot me an email and i will see if i can get the item for you thanks and have a wonderful day http://www.fourbrosoutdoor.com
Do you have and Klick?  Ill check out the store. Good luck on your ventures! I like the name!
